{"tid":1621521,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消毒組係時候做野啦!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-04T13:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T21:14:21.000Z","uid":147785,"like":729,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"3fefda519035d0d1afe6b86025acab866f0fe5a9","tid":1621521,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"我知大家今日打得好爽<br />\n<br />\n亦支持繼續18區開花<br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記國際戰線要繼續維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地咁爆法 畫面一定就難睇 但唔代表要唔做<br />\n<br />\n所以twitter, reddit, 文宣組係時候幫勇武消毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋請推 智利仔 個直播channel 比國際<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JJEC3MmuJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4JJEC3MmuJ8&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d75720b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JJEC3MmuJ8</a><br />\n<br />\n智利仔識<span style=\"color: red;\">聽廣東話</span>,會<span style=\"color: red;\">翻譯記者講既野</span>,而且佢跟得好貼, 直播會<span style=\"color: red;\">解釋示威者行為背後既原因目的</span><br />\n<br />\n重點係用英文直播 英文極流利 仲會ban 一切5毛留言<br />\n<br />\n如果推得爆佢個直播channel 絕對可以有效減輕事後消毒既工作<br />\n<br />\n因為佢會一邊直播一邊幫我地消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後附上佢之前唱既榮光<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRFRm1_GUps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsRFRm1_GUps&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=2b87a3d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRFRm1_GUps</a>"},{"pid":"32244b15bdb3afd50ef6eead99ca084548d76b1e","tid":1621521,"uid":271434,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"},{"pid":"9d8d21150563b02bf33a1b12e51bcb04b9e3aa1c","tid":1621521,"uid":322230,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"大家有冇諗過幪面法係針對記者"},{"pid":"75040316acf98e65dbea61fd9d0c011d83118111","tid":1621521,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"推，急需"},{"pid":"d992805e8e4525a4600a39b14e291c710b1c7ef1","tid":1621521,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7aea9656b19119ae52949ae447da3d28b20d5e1","tid":1621521,"uid":62714,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"國際點會唔支持 <br />\n未見過幾年前烏克蘭點咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過文宣的確要做下"},{"pid":"fc57508b0abfcd6ab8272e95b6e2b10752876537","tid":1621521,"uid":35456,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7432e85d13b6faab59cf07ac980520e0a22967d","tid":1621521,"uid":147785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b7aea9656b19119ae52949ae447da3d28b